---
title: Squash and Kale Flatbread with Sausage and Caramelized Onion
description: Hearty kale, sweet butternut squash, and savoury sausage come together in a pizza trifecta. Flavoured with caramelized onions and covered with a blanket of mozzarella, this dish is bound to become your classic go-to.
